init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: People were losing their minds - everywhere we went, we would see people screaming at one another, fighting over the proper order of "Dad-

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was as if the whole world had completely lost their minds all at once.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I guess that does bring a little bit of good out of it, right?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The answer is still a huge mystery.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There are a lot of theories about it, of course, and everyone has an opinion.
